  &lt;img class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-image css-0&quot; alt=&quot;Research methods stickies&quot; title=&quot;Stickies time&quot; src=&quot;/gatsby-min/static/7dce03ec3f6eac716ed2b6e6f1ca4fd9/18e3b/david-travis-WC6MJ0kRzGw-unsplash.jpg&quot; srcSet=&quot;/gatsby-min/static/7dce03ec3f6eac716ed2b6e6f1ca4fd9/46946/david-travis-WC6MJ0kRzGw-unsplash.jpg 240w,/gatsby-min/static/7dce03ec3f6eac716ed2b6e6f1ca4fd9/55489/david-travis-WC6MJ0kRzGw-unsplash.jpg 480w,/gatsby-min/static/7dce03ec3f6eac716ed2b6e6f1ca4fd9/18e3b/david-travis-WC6MJ0kRzGw-unsplash.jpg 960w,/gatsby-min/static/7dce03ec3f6eac716ed2b6e6f1ca4fd9/60e21/david-travis-WC6MJ0kRzGw-unsplash.jpg 1440w,/gatsby-min/static/7dce03ec3f6eac716ed2b6e6f1ca4fd9/69b48/david-travis-WC6MJ0kRzGw-unsplash.jpg 1920w,/gatsby-min/static/7dce03ec3f6eac716ed2b6e6f1ca4fd9/bb9a8/david-travis-WC6MJ0kRzGw-unsplash.jpg 2560w&quot; sizes=&quot;(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px&quot; style=&quot;width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0&quot; loading=&quot;lazy&quot;/&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 class=&quot;css-1p1kpni&quot;&gt;Discover shared objectives (Align)&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;style data-emotion-css=&quot;14fixdb&quot;&gt;.css-14fixdb{font-family:inherit;font-weight:700;line-height:1.25;margin:0;margin-bottom:0.25rem;font-size:1.25rem;color:var(--theme-ui-colors-heading,#000);margin-top:1rem;}@media screen and (min-width:640px){.css-14fixdb{font-size:1.5rem;}}@media screen and (min-width:768px){.css-14fixdb{font-size:1.5rem;}}@media screen and (min-width:1024px){.css-14fixdb{font-size:1.875rem;}}&lt;/style&gt;&lt;h4 class=&quot;css-14fixdb&quot;&gt;Opportunities to improve&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;css-1ccrm8j&quot;&gt;Design most wanted to improve in these areas:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul class=&quot;css-15rlv7r&quot;&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;css-0&quot;&gt;Understand the criteria for making decisions about what user needs and features to prioritize&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;css-0&quot;&gt;Prioritize improvements to the user experience currently considered out of scope&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;css-1ccrm8j&quot;&gt;Product hoped to improve:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul class=&quot;css-15rlv7r&quot;&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;css-0&quot;&gt;Maintain forward momentum on prioritized work&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;css-0&quot;&gt;Keep the schedule predictable&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h4 class=&quot;css-14fixdb&quot;&gt;Aligning identified needs&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;css-1ccrm8j&quot;&gt;I determined that the teams&amp;#x27; requests centered on:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul class=&quot;css-15rlv7r&quot;&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;css-0&quot;&gt;&lt;em class=&quot;css-0&quot;&gt;Align&lt;/em&gt; on decision criteria&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;css-0&quot;&gt;&lt;em class=&quot;css-0&quot;&gt;Align&lt;/em&gt; on decisions made over the course of the initiative.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;css-0&quot;&gt;&lt;em class=&quot;css-0&quot;&gt;Create predictability&lt;/em&gt; in time required to conduct research and execute design tasks&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li cla